OL,4,Cdevice in his skull in world first
OL,6,FOran has enjoyed a much better quality
OL,7,Fof life since having the surgery, as
OL,8,FITV News Health Correspondent Rebecca
OL,9,FBarry reports
OL,11,FA British teenager with severe
OL,12,Fepilepsy has become the first person
OL,13,Fin the world to trial a revolutionary
OL,14,Fdevice implanted into his skull.
OL,16,FOran Knowlson, from Somerset, received
OL,17,Fsurgery at Great Ormand Street
OL,18,FHospital after he experienced seizures
OL,19,Fthat "robbed him of his childhood"
OL,20,Fwith often life-threatening instances.
