OL,4,Cdevice in his skull in world first
OL,6,FOran, who has Lennox-Gastaut syndrome,
OL,7,Fa rare form of epilepsy, has struggled
OL,8,Fwith these daily seizures since the
OL,9,Fage of three.
OL,11,FThe neurostimulator has reduced Oran's
OL,12,Fdaytime seizures by 80%, greatly
OL,13,Fincreasing his quality of life.
OL,15,FOran's mum Justine said: "We've tried
OL,16,Feverything, but this is the first real
OL,17,Fshot we've been given in years, there
OL,18,Fhas been no 'what next' until now."
