OL,6,FThe breakthrough is part of the CADET
OL,7,Fproject, a series of trials that
OL,8,Fassesses the safety and effectiveness
OL,9,Fof deep-brain stimulation for severe
OL,10,Fepilepsy.
OL,12,F"The future looks hopeful which I
OL,13,Fwouldn't have dreamed of saying six
OL,14,Fmonths ago. For Oran, having hope
OL,15,Fbrings excitement," his mum said.
OL,17,FHow does the device work?
