OL,6,FEpilepsy seizures can be triggered by
OL,7,Fabnormal bursts of electrical activity
OL,8,Fin the brain. The device sends
OL,9,Fcurrents deep into the brain and aims
OL,10,Fto block or disrupt these abnormal
OL,11,Fsignals.
OL,13,FThe surgery took place in October 2023
OL,14,Fand a team led by consultant
OL,15,Fpaediatric neurosurgeon Martin Tisdall
OL,16,Fperformed the eight-hour surgery.
OL,18,FThey inserted electrodes into Oran's
OL,19,Fbrain until they reached the thalamus,
OL,20,Fa key hub for neural information.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
